<section id="features" style="padding:80px 5%">
  <div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto">
    <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 0">
      <span class="sec-label">Fonctionnalités</span>
      <h2>Tout ce dont un trader <em>sérieux</em> a besoin</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-grid rstag">
      <div class="feat-card featured">
        <span class="feat-num">01</span>
        <div class="feat-ico" style="background:rgba(16,185,129,.09)">☀️</div>
        <h3>Pré-session matin</h3>
        <p>Mood check, recap de la veille avec phrase IA, objectifs de la semaine rappelés avant de trader.</p>
        <span class="feat-tag tag-free">✓ Gratuit</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card featured">
        <span class="feat-num">02</span>
        <div class="feat-ico" style="background:rgba(59,130,246,.09)">⚡</div>
        <h3>Session live</h3>
        <p>Live feed de tes trades en temps réel. Logger un trade en 3 secondes. Clôture avec détection SL/TP/Manuel automatique.</p>
        <span class="feat-tag tag-free">✓ Gratuit</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card featured">
        <span class="feat-num">03</span>
        <div class="feat-ico" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,.09)">📅</div>
        <h3>Calendrier éco IA</h3>
        <p>Events économiques filtrés pour tes actifs. Quand un résultat tombe, l'IA analyse immédiatement : bull ou bear pour NQ, BTC, EUR/USD.</p>
        <span class="feat-tag tag-prem">★ Premium</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <span class="feat-num">04</span>
        <div class="feat-ico" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,.09)">🌙</div>
        <h3>Recap journalier 17h30</h3>
        <p>Email automatique à la clôture des marchés — P&amp;L, win rate, émotion dominante, phrase coaching IA personnalisée.</p>
        <span class="feat-tag tag-prem">★ Premium</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <span class="feat-num">05</span>
        <div class="feat-ico" style="background:rgba(34,211,238,.09)">💬</div>
        <h3>Coach IA qui te connaît</h3>
        <p>Tu définis ton profil une fois — scalper ICT, day trader SMC, swing trader Price Action. L'IA intègre ce contexte dans chaque analyse.</p>
        <span class="feat-tag tag-prem">★ Premium</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <span class="feat-num">06</span>
        <div class="feat-ico" style="background:rgba(59,130,246,.09)">📊</div>
        <h3>Analytics avancés</h3>
        <p>Heatmap horaire, equity curve, drawdown max, top actifs, performance par setup. Tout ce qu'un prop trader professionnel suit.</p>
        <span class="feat-tag tag-prem">★ Premium</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <span class="feat-num">07</span>
        <div class="feat-ico" style="background:rgba(99,155,255,.09)">📤</div>
        <h3>Import CSV universel</h3>
        <p>Tradovate, Binance, MetaTrader, Bybit ou n'importe quel broker. Il détecte et structure ton historique automatiquement.</p>
        <span class="feat-tag tag-free">✓ Gratuit</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <span class="feat-num">08</span>
        <div class="feat-ico" style="background:rgba(245,166,35,.09)">🏆</div>
        <h3>Score trader /100</h3>
        <p>Score hebdomadaire sur 5 axes — discipline, risque, consistance, émotions, performance. Suis ta progression réelle.</p>
        <span class="feat-tag tag-prem">★ Premium</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <span class="feat-num">09</span>
        <div class="feat-ico" style="background:rgba(16,185,129,.09)">⚙️</div>
        <h3>Multi-marché natif</h3>
        <p>Futures CME (NQ, ES, MES, Gold, 6E), Crypto spot/levier, Forex, Indices CFD. P&amp;L exact en ticks avec multiplicateurs officiels.</p>
        <span class="feat-tag tag-free">✓ Gratuit</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .feat-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 36px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .feat-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--b);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px;
    transition: border-color .2s, transform .2s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .feat-card:hover { border-color: var(--b2); transform: translateY(-3px); }
  .feat-card.featured { border-color: rgba(34,211,238,.25); background: linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(34,211,238,.04),rgba(59,130,246,.04)); }

  .feat-num {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--txt3);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
  }

  .feat-ico {
    width: 42px; height: 42px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .feat-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--disp);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: -.2px;
  }

  .feat-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--txt2);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .feat-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .tag-free { background: rgba(16,185,129,.1);  color: var(--green); border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.2); }
  .tag-prem { background: rgba(59,130,246,.1);  color: var(--blue2); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.2); }
  .tag-new  { background: rgba(245,158,11,.1);  color: var(--yel);   border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.2); }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) and (min-width: 769px) {
    .feat-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .feat-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    .feat-card { padding: 20px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .feat-card { padding: 18px 16px; }
  }
</style>
